main event: A white metallic sphere-shaped object was observed for one hour and forty minutes in Indian House, NWT, Canada.
interesting points: The object was the size of an aircraft and disappeared by being obscured by clouds., Insufficient information provided for a proper analysis of the sighting., The sighting was only recorded visually with no photographs captured., The object was seen in a reported scattered cloud condition., The report indicates that it could possibly be a balloon or an aircraft.
